{"tid":357885,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實英國皇室同納粹真係有千絲萬縷既關係？？","createTime":"2017-08-13T10:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T09:46:51.000Z","uid":10338,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4691b9b5194b09fcf4d348179054471d04bff0","tid":357885,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"前排話溫莎公爵係因為親納粹<br />\n先做唔到英王<br />\n而且sun 之前post過張相係英女王細個做納粹手勢<br />\n聽神秘之夜講 邱吉爾二戰果陣一直同王室博奕緊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70007ea46868187655f9804652b947f24e1dc412","tid":357885,"uid":34284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"我正係知依家英國王室本姓係德國姓氏，其後改姓windsor"},{"pid":"6d589b9c8ffc0a87321d01230da252ae3481f737","tid":357885,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"當年元首同蘇聯簽左好多秘密條約出賣盟軍"},{"pid":"b9c588ecd99967cd690308f7d28e99e27e8bc1bf","tid":357885,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我正係知依家英國王室本姓係德國姓氏，其後改姓windsor</blockquote><br />\n因為同德國佬打一戰嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 表示同德國佬切割"},{"pid":"a2f9de6a7b127be57cf1c904d2dad43df4925084","tid":357885,"uid":16892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:12:25.000Z","msg":"其實英文都係日耳曼語系"},{"pid":"3e5db8b9fda8803605b91d19fad847f39c7a352d","tid":357885,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:13:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89590dbbaa705cafc4e7b10f7d94e8a5686ac897","tid":357885,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我正係知依家英國王室本姓係德國姓氏，其後改姓windsor</blockquote><br />\n因為同德國佬打一戰嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 表示同德國佬切割</blockquote><br />\n同歐洲皇室計血脈冇乜意義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差唔多全部歐洲國家皇室都有親戚關係"},{"pid":"9ec5077fff3c02448527ecc1008663a42be13b72","tid":357885,"uid":100883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T20:39:30.000Z","msg":"建議可以睇下歷史<br />\n皇室本身係有繼承姓氏傳統，就算無繼承都會有跟父姓，係當時皇室與皇室聯婚係非常普遍事情，而且大多係指定。<br />\n<br />\n而當時二戰德國皇室已經好似無左（一戰時廢除及其資產被人充公），所以無咩關係<br />\n<br />\n另外，英女王當時做納粹手勢，只係當時未知納粹本身做嘅事，二戰時英皇室已經好快同納粹劃清界線。而戰爭時候英軍長期處於劣勢，可以相信皇室有講和派係不足為奇，但鄧寇克大行動令邱吉爾唔講和決心大增，皇室成員有出賣國家行動都不為奇，不過一定唔係主要皇室成員，可以睇到英政府與皇室有角力，但都影響唔到邱吉爾<br />\n<br />\n英國皇室生存到而家係有佢作用同能力，英國人對皇室尊敬，就知道地位係國內有崇高地位。"},{"pid":"f9cc015c762c2acd9edb6bf0355bc0f01cc76992","tid":357885,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f6bf6d3eb66b1cffc4d17d425cc69aebca4547","tid":357885,"uid":126897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T09:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實英文都係日耳曼語系</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/English_language\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FEnglish_language&d=MR2cyq34YS3YJ7OZFMm7IwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=606ce06a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/English_language</a>"}]}